nyh.png\" width=\"700\" alt=\"Masky Enchanted Items\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xb3xpd.png\" width=750/> </p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/zuywca.png\"/width=\"500\">\n</p>\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>Accessibility</summary>\n\n\n[Curseforge](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/enchantment-outlines)\n\n\n[Cit resewn required under 1.21.4](https://modrinth.com/mod/cit-resewn)\n\n\n[Sodium Compatible](https://modrinth.com/mod/sodium)\n\nTixul's Enchantment Outlines.\n\n\n[25% off server hosting. Use code \"DANI\" for 25% off.\n](https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=3073)\n\nABOUT: \nAdds a stylish, vibrant outline to every enchanted tool. Inspired by Actions & Stuff.\n\nFEATURES:\nRespackopts compatibility options. 3D bows and maces. Compatibility with most shader packs.\n\nOTHER:\nFeatured by DemonJoeTV\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/gEnrM4tDtmM\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\nWant colours other than pink? Try [MaskyEnchantedItems!](https://www.google.com/search?q=maskyenchanteditems)\n\nCREDITS:\nOreville Studios: The main inspiration behind this pack.\nRadiational: Helped with bow models.\nPatovskiz: Helped create backport. \nnot_thefirst: Helped with backport and shaders.\nCubert1: Took some gallery images.\n</details>\n\n",
